rows.name: Cole-san's health seems to be getting better.

rows.label: tlk43420341_06_msg0002
rows.name:
Nothing I could do to help...
But I knew you'd come through.

rows.label: tlk43420341_06_msg0003
rows.name:
I want to show there's more to
mercenaries than people think.

rows.label: tlk43420341_06_msg0004
rows.name:
You know, by doing the right thing
by anyone who needs help.

rows.label: tlk43420341_06_msg0005
rows.name:
You know, the kind of thing that
Vandham would have approved of.
